    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，参与者是Alice、Bob和John三位。Alice先给John发消息\"Hello John, how are you?\"，然后John有个自我循环的Healthcheck环节，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
