    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，那个循环是John在跟自己的疑病症作斗争，所以是John指向John自己的消息。循环结束后，我想在John右侧加个注释，说明理性思维最终占了上风。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "John-John",
        "Fight against hypochondria",
        "Note right of John",
        "Rational thoughts"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我加上loop Healthcheck，里面是John自己发给自己的\"Fight against hypochondria\"，然后在John右侧标注\"Rational thoughts prevail\"。接下来John回复Alice？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "loop Healthcheck",
        "John-John",
        "Note right of John"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "是的，John用虚线箭头回复Alice\"Great!\"，然后再用实线箭头问Bob\"How about you?\"，最后Bob用虚线回复\"Jolly good!\"。注意Bob的回复要用虚线。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "John--Alice",
        "Great",
