      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确认一下：John给Alice是虚线回复\"Great!\"，给Bob是实线提问\"How about you?\"，然后Bob虚线回\"Jolly good!\"。这里John问Bob用实线，是因为开启新话题？",
